text: Trophocosta maculifera is a species of moth of the family Tortricidae. It is found in Vietnam. Adults are similar to Trophocosta tucki, and may even be its junior synonym.A catalogue of type specimens of the Tortricidae described by V. I. Kuznetzov from Vietnam and deposited in the Zoological Institute, St. Petersburg ==References== Category:Moths described in 1992 Category:Tortricini
title: Trophocosta maculifera
